snippet.title: New Upcoming MMORPG 2023! Monster Saga : Evolution Gameplay
snippet.description:
Start the Adventure with Cute Pets!
MMORPG 2023, another world adventure "Monster Saga: Evolution" is coming soon!
Invite your Pet and friends to go on an adventure in another world!
Explore the mysterious story of the Continent of Light together and write your own legend along the way!

Invite your Pet and friends to go on an adventure in another world!

Pre-registration Benefit 1--Exclusive Gifts!
⭐Limited Decorations, get it after pre-registration!
⭐God Pet SSR option, get Gacha 100x for free with continuous login!
⭐Mysterious Rainbow Diamond system, free gifts are waiting for you!

Pre-registration Benefit 2--Claim an Exclusive Mount for free for a limited time
⭐Get it when pre-registration reaches 20K people--Shells*100; Low Training Manual*5; Stardust Fragments*5
⭐Get it when pre-registration reaches 50K people--Shells*200; Enhance Breakthrough Stone*3; Stardust Fragments*10
⭐Get it when pre-registration reaches 100K people--Shells*200; Pet SSR Fragments*10; Pet SR Fragments*20
⭐ Get it when pre-registration reaches 150K people--Shells*200; Divination Coupon*10; Pet SR Fragments*30
⭐Get it when pre-registration reaches 200K people-- Exclusive Mounts*1; Orange Clothes Chest Lv.30*1; Low-Soul Stone Treasure Chest*1; Treasure Hunt Coupon*1

Download & Pre-registration:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.eyougame.ynqj

Facebook Page :
https://www.facebook.com/eyoumse?mibextid=ZbWKwL

#MonsterSagaEvolution #MMORPG2023
